    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/42d1794ee711c4039095403159acfa22.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GABANG: ULTIMATE</strong>是一款Roguelike构筑牌组游戏，您可以使用包中的物品击败敌人，并建造自己的牌组。在收到女神的礼物--一个拥有神秘力量、能容纳无限物品的袋子后，你踏上了打败恶魔的冒险之旅。您能全身而退到达诅咒之地并打败恶魔吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/1cd1764718a5549b521cf2815da1d1c9.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过<strong>350</strong>多种不同的物品和多个职业，您可以打造自己的牌组!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/b18807022482df2f6102c30edb9b6a07.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用收集到的物品随机组合杀死敌!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/4c3c7e68e393536c6c8faf356f240103.poster.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/4c3c7e68e393536c6c8faf356f240103.webm?t=1744900682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/4c3c7e68e393536c6c8faf356f240103.mp4?t=1744900682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成不同的成就，获得不同的皮肤!</p>",
